    <item>
      <title>塔利班拒绝特朗普归还价值数十亿美元的美国武器的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taliban-rejects-trump-s-call-to-return-us-weapons-worth-billions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士表示，塔利班不会归还美军在 2021 年撤离阿富汗时留下的任何军事装备，因为喀布尔和唐纳德·特朗普政府之间的关系开始变得不稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taliban-rejects-trump-s-call-to-return-us-weapons-worth-billions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:12:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾军方称“外国势力”试图控制菲律宾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/-foreign-power-attempting-to-map-out-philippines-military-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方表示，继上周逮捕一名中国间谍嫌疑人并在其海域发现多架无人机后，一个“外国势力”可能正试图绘制这个东南亚国家的地图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/-foreign-power-attempting-to-map-out-philippines-military-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克新任财政部长上任第一天就面临债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mozambique-s-new-finance-chief-faces-debt-headache-from-day-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任财政部长卡拉·洛韦拉（Carla Louveira）接手的国库因数月的动乱而变得虚弱，而且还要应对潜在的债务重组和政府雇员的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mozambique-s-new-finance-chief-faces-debt-headache-from-day-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将与特朗普政府一起提高对拜登人工智能芯片的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-to-raise-biden-s-ai-chip-curbs-with-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟将对美国限制英伟达等公司向其部分成员国出口人工智能芯片的决定向美国提出担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-to-raise-biden-s-ai-chip-curbs-with-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:31:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
